overview: Kat Robichaud and The Darling Misfits present Bite, a vampire themed Rock cabaret featuring many covers of well known songs, as well as several new original songs. Featuring costumes based on Bram Stoker's Dracula, Nosferatu, Buffy the Vampire Slayer, and From Dusk til' Dawn.
title: Misfit Cabaret Presents Bite
